<a class="anchor" id="application.get"></a>
<div class="documentation">
  <h3>GET /application</h3>
  <p>Returns the current application's information. The amount of information retrieved depends on the current authentication scope. A client with admin auth scope will return all the information about the app, any lower level auth scope will just return public information:</p>
  <pre><code class="http">GET https://api.marketcloud.it/v0/application</code></pre>
    
  <div class="spacer"></div>  
    
  <h5>Example JSON response (200) with admin scope</h5>
  <pre><code class="javascript">{
"status": true,
"data": [
